{"tid":172663,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣 (101) 真正的惡魔 正是無限膨脹的民意","createTime":"2017-03-26T04:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T04:55:45.000Z","uid":34156,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a285a1866a8b9bd12b497b99ed04456c39e7f15","tid":172663,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">溫馨提示：頭post出齊先好留名</span></strong></span><br />\n🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/h2wGUB6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh2wGUB6.gif&h=610d5079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EDjJ9nQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEDjJ9nQ.jpg&h=4443e715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾個月嘅時光 眨下眼就過左<br />\n希望大家可以keep住呢份熱情<br />\n即使大家係唔同既地方<br />\n都係喺同一個天空下 喜歡同一個結衣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>標題來源<br />\ncb、heavenly days 歌詞</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FH5P790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFH5P790.jpg&h=720f6adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQY1CY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQY1CY3.jpg&h=e0f785a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1k0AfRa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1k0AfRa.png&h=68333130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <blockquote>▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼<br />\n- 全舊post連結：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/GEzE2n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FGEzE2n&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=40916aa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/GEzE2n</a><br />\n- 近期消息整合：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/O3I76l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FO3I76l&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=fd9d6a77\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/O3I76l</a><br />\n-新post格式：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/1RJM5F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F1RJM5F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d9ad2434\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/1RJM5F</a><br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2樓入門攻略、投票區、綜藝<br />\n廣告、相集、Google drive綜合下載</strong></span><br />\n- 3樓新劇/電影資訊<br />\n▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>3月23&amp;24日新SP！！<br />\n《羈絆～奔跑吧！奇蹟的小馬～》</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVhD1G8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVhD1G8.jpg&h=849e0da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ts00fs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ts00fs.jpg&h=7ba0d6ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://www.nhk.or.jp/dsp/kizuna/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhk.or.jp%2Fdsp%2Fkizuna%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5fb8edc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhk.or.jp/dsp/kizuna/</a><br />\nPV：<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9037719/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav9037719%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=eaaa5917\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9037719/</a><br />\n<br />\n出演：<br />\n役所広司、新垣結衣、岡田將生<br />\n勝地涼、小林薫、田中裕子</div><br />\n<br />\n　　<span style=\"color: red;\">本作品，是東日本大震災受傷的一家，各種困難和戰鬥的同時，地震日出生的小馬夢想的賽馬到成長的身姿，福島縣的相馬舞台壓倒性的描繪的SP電視劇。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　東日本大地震失去了長子的拓馬（岡田將生）的家人，和地震當日出生的小馬相依為命。父親&middot;雅之（役所廣司）和長女&middot;將子（新垣結衣）想將死去的哥哥夢見的競技馬培育起來，母親&middot;佳世子（田中裕子）沉浸在失去了長子的悲痛之中無法自拔。以前是騎手的青年&middot;夏雄（勝地涼）與協助他家人，進行受災地的復興，同時也依靠著作為北海道的牧場主人的加山（小林薰）。於是家庭面臨嚴峻的現實。真的是夢寐以求的競技馬就能夠跑起來嗎？<br />\n廣播：NHK 2017年3月23及24日（前後篇．各73分）<br />\n<br />\n前篇(字幕)：<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9351185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav9351185&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=40cdb640\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9351185</a><br />\n後篇(字幕)：<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9372173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav9372173&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=42c0a766\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av9372173</a>"},{"pid":"58db91f1d4d9e221649792a7f14f112440b8e795","tid":172663,"uid":82661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"第一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a93a60716459917e695f105d52f788dd81c787f","tid":172663,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>新手上路主線攻略：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/TnYOcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FTnYOcs&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f236fa9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/TnYOcs</a><br />\n<br />\n歷年LIHKG會員投票參考<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/WfECpU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FWfECpU&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=612bc48f\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/WfECpU</a><br />\n<br />\nB站Gakki綜藝連結<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/0h1G6W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F0h1G6W&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=43010967\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/0h1G6W</a><br />\n<br />\nGakki全廣告(Google Drive)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/nrQvmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnrQvmQ&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5E