"https://na.cx/i/97B91eP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97B91eP.jpg&h=61a86686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TB523R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TB523R.jpg&h=c72bb608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n腳本：古沢良太（Legal High 腳本）<br />\n監督：石川淳一（Legal High 監督）<br />\n<br />\n共演卡司：広末涼子、遠藤憲一、田中美佐子、佐野勇斗、瀬戸康史、永野芽郁、蒼井優、森崎博之、吉田鋼太郎、生瀬勝久、山口紗彌加、斎藤司、久間田琳加、鈴木福、谷花音、真木よう子、小日向文世等。<br />\n<br />\n 2月中旬開始攝影，2017年秋全國東寶系公開！ 新垣結衣飾演戀愛和工作都很失敗的原天才乒乓球少女、快30歲的單身OL富田多滿子，與瑛太飾演的原日本職業拳擊手組合成乒乓球混雙，向全國大賽挑戰的故事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>《Code Blue 3》製作決定!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/100302_53bdee902bf86890010775dc3176e6ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F100302_53bdee902bf86890010775dc3176e6ed.jpg&h=039dc2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月開拍，時間設定於第2季的七年後，播放時間：7月份 月九<br />\n<br />\n十年過去，各人都走上自己的人生道路。<br />\n<br />\n藍沢耕作（山下智久）離開咗翔陽大學附屬醫院嘅急症室之後，喺腦外科深造研究，目標係成為最強嘅腦外科醫生。<br />\n<br />\n白石恵（新垣結衣）就繼續喺人手不足嘅翔北急症室工作，成為咗飛行救護團隊嘅領導醫生奮鬥中！<br />\n<br />\n緋山美帆子（戸田恵梨香）就去咗備產醫療中心，喺婦產科果度深造。<br />\n<br />\n冴島はるか（比嘉愛未）依家繼續做緊飛行團隊嘅護士。<br />\n<br />\n藤川一男（浅利洋介）同白石一齊留咗喺翔北急症室，只係自己向着成為整形外科嘅急症室醫生之路進發。<br />\n<br />\n面臨新挑戰，失去家人，開始戀愛，在新嘅階段有邊個對手等緊佢哋？<br />\n<br />\n來自 Gakki 的訊息：<br />\n<br />\n  「在最初的《Code Blue》拍攝中收到的20歲生日祝福，好像已經過了很久，又像是最近的事。在這20代的最後一年再次扮演白石惠，以及劇組時隔7年的集結，感受到極大的緣分和使命感。全新的《Code Blue》故事中，狀況、立場、所有的事物都有很大的改變，當時一起努力著的5人會有什麼發展我非常期待。希望能讓觀眾看得開心，也希望能夠有所收穫，我會全力以赴的！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ricgrady.pixnet.net/blog/post/117081740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fricgrady.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F117081740&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=548828b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://ricgrady.pixnet.net/blog/post/117081740</a>"},{"pid":"da3a421da55eb7194645561c37fce2b2e8103a11","tid":172663,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc7e3cd4ae00f9119bafa6d22660d98b23799cb","tid":172663,"uid":8542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">完</span></span>"},{"pid":"5bd42a732cd43cc0005d462a569abb0f549ff28b","tid":172663,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"唔係仲有一層咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mhdDm8B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmhdDm8B.gif&h=0b8f8d01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"933e81062a670edc59d95959e988ac41a2d0708d","tid":172663,"uid":79954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b1bbd6575e5a8fac8edd9bd00805326ae4849d","tid":172663,"uid":22080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e42c80354666e213249bd1cb904fe809daa2d94","tid":172663,"uid":65321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/FMIxtEc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFMIxtEc.jpg&h=0c16f79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留名"},{"pid":"6852b48a7ba78542a852e04d5fc96684353a0a15","tid":172663,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T04:34:43.000Z","msg":"個個都唔守規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dda752f0d1ca8eb07c74301859